            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d04f934b-d239-4ff9-8712-42688b40d058">
                Mr. Chamberlain
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d04f934b-d239-4ff9-8712-42688b40d058" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
