            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-989b41a1-f395-4858-9178-bf71f3fdcfe4">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Attlee)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-989b41a1-f395-4858-9178-bf71f3fdcfe4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
