    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As no official communication has been addressed to me by either President Truman or Marshal Stalin, I see no purpose in intervening as suggested by the hon. Member.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-989b41a1-f395-4858-9178-bf71f3fdcfe4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
